{"id":582147,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/04/【网络民议】圣经成禁书？网友热传全网下架/","date":"2018-04-03T12:20:09Z","modified":"2018-04-04T07:48:55Z","title":"【网络民议】圣经成禁书？网友热传“全网下架”","content":"<p>近日，在社交网络上陆续有网友反映，在中国国内的淘宝、京东、当当网、亚马逊等网络电商平台，已无法搜索并购买到《圣经》，疑似已遭全网下架。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ShepherdChow/status/980997167572758528\">https://twitter.com/ShepherdChow/status/980997167572758528</a></p>\n<p>目前，在淘宝搜索“圣经”，反馈的结果仅为解读、评论、辞典、书皮等相关内容，而无法搜索到圣经原本，当当网、亚马逊也是同样情况。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DZ0zj2EVAAUnFGU-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-582150\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DZ0zj2EVAAUnFGU-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"605\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DZ0zj2EVAAUnFGU-1.jpg 750w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DZ0zj2EVAAUnFGU-1-223x300.jpg 223w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>而在京东搜索“圣经”，则无任何结果显示，但相应地英文搜索“holy bible”却可以显示结果。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DZ1cqZVVMAEo1xI.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-582151\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DZ1cqZVVMAEo1xI.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DZ1cqZVVMAEo1xI.jpg 675w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DZ1cqZVVMAEo1xI-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/DZ1cqZVVMAEo1xI-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>从谷歌图片检索结果看，不少淘宝店铺确实曾上架过《圣经》,但目前这些商品链接均已失效。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-582152\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"241\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索.jpg 1912w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索-300x131.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索-768x336.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索-1024x448.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-582153\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"197\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索2.jpg 1072w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索2-300x107.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索2-768x274.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/圣经检索2-1024x366.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有不少网友通过自己的网络检索或从社交圈传言“验证”了此事。有网友提到（未证实说法），现版《圣经》或将收到内容审查和重编。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">中国于2018年3月30号起全网下架所有《圣经》销售，其中淘宝、京东、微<br />店、当当网、亚马逊一本圣经也买不到。相关基督教书籍也陆续封杀、店铺被销<br />户。 <a href=\"https://t.co/rqt5qXvC7y\">pic.twitter.com/rqt5qXvC7y</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 🐳 (@Uromayutori) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Uromayutori/status/981049092469067777?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"und\" dir=\"ltr\">. <a href=\"https://t.co/9xRt119hmE\">pic.twitter.com/9xRt119hmE</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Monica &#8211; Major Tom (@Chinaive_New) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Chinaive_New/status/981068928477794304?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>https://twitter.com/sailingger/status/981041978367332353</p>\n<p>https://twitter.com/zwitterion2018/status/981101401156628480</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">圣经本体，中英对照本确实下架了…还好我买的两本发货了…感谢主！ <a href=\"https://t.co/IAfjiymD73\">pic.twitter.com/IAfjiymD73</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 水熊台长 (@wlandzh) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/wlandzh/status/981053315021705216?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">查了下华严经，法华经，楞严经还在卖，古兰经和圣训也有货。这次专干基督徒</p>\n<p>&mdash; lebao wu🇦🇺 (@MerlotN) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MerlotN/status/981058723274637312?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">這些都是在計畫之中，下架也是有原因的，在中國基督教五年工作規劃裡面就有提到「加强圣经研究，建立正确的圣经观与符合处境的释经学是深化神学思想建设的基础。要有意识培养圣经研究人才，为着手重译圣经或编写圣经注释打下坚实基础。」估計要出版中國化後的聖經！</p>\n<p>&mdash; Jacob Lee (@JacobLeewb) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/JacobLeewb/status/981140262213664768?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,17016],"tags":[34250,34248,9249,34251,34249]}